decks.notes: This deck focuses on utilizing artifacts to quickly build up a board presence and apply continuous pressure on the opponent. By playing efficient artifact creatures like Voldaren Epicure and Spyglass Siren, combined with powerful artifact spells like Ensoul Artifact and Shrapnel Blast, the deck aims to overwhelm the opponent early in the game. The inclusion of Jegantha, the Wellspring as a companion provides additional versatility and mana fixing. Overall, the strategy revolves around aggressive plays and leveraging the synergy between artifacts to secure a swift victory.
